OL,6,FA Guernsey man is on trial for alleged
OL,7,Fhistorical sexual offences of primary
OL,8,Fschool-aged children.
OL,10,FMichael Derek Cotterill, 82, appeared
OL,11,Fbefore the Royal Court of Guernsey on
OL,12,FMonday 6 January 2025.
OL,14,FHe is facing eight charges for alleged
OL,15,Foffences between the years 1988 and
OL,16,F1991.
OL,18,FThe two complainants were both of
OL,19,Fprimary school age at the time of the
OL,20,Falleged offences.
